lead_paragraph: Former Tour de France winner Bjarne Riis and Lars Seier Christensen, co-owner of online forex brokerage Saxo Bank, have become part of the group of owners of the Danish third-tier cycling team Team Virtu Pro-Veloconcept.

headline.print_headline: Former Tour Winner Riis Buys Into Danish Cycling Team
headline.main: Former Tour Winner Riis Buys Into Danish Cycling Team
